          "Student-wise 7:3 split; temporal order preserved; 5-fold CV; padded/truncated to length 500; QQQ-matrix smoothing γ=0.03",
          "DKT, AKT, SAINT+, LPKT, GCKT",
          "5-Fold Cross-Validation",
          "MOOCRadar: \n{AUC: 0.8602 - GCKT}\n\nMath: \n{AUC: 0.8615 - GGCKT}\n\n\n",
          "Main contribution is better fusion of temporal + hierarchical knowledge features; also somewhat interpretable via gate-weight analysis",
          "Needs rich cognitive annotations; cold start and very long sequences remain issues\n\n"
